item.title: Username Enumeratoin With Python and Mutillidae
item.description: sudo apt-get install docker docker-compose git clone https://github.com/webpwnized/mutillidae-dockerhub.git cd mutillidae-dockerhub/ sudo docker-compose up When I was preparing for my GPEN exam, I searched online (a lot) to find some useful hints. What is the difference between SANS and GIAC? SANS Institute specializes in Information and Cyber Security training, it was founded in 1898. Simply it’s the body that provides training services. On the other hand, GIAC is the entity that is responsible for the examination.
